data.description:
Gracefully placed on a corner lot in prime location, this beauty is far from ordinary. With a thoughtful split floor plan, it's designed to offer both privacy and functionality, making it an ideal family home. Situated strategically, this property is close enough to all essential services and amenities, yet it remains unaffected by the hustle and bustle of traffic. This ensures that you have quick and easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment, while still enjoying a peaceful and serene atmosphere. The split floor plan places the primary bedroom on one side of the house, offering a retreat for relaxation, while the remaining two bedrooms are thoughtfully situated on the opposite side, providing privacy and separation for family members and guests. The heart of the home is the spacious family room, where a magnificent brick fireplace graces one wall from top to bottom. This cozy, rustic feature is bound to become the focal point for countless cherished moments. The dining area, open to the family room, offers a wonderful space for gatherings, ensuring that you can entertain with ease. The well-maintained yard surrounding the house not only adds to its curb appeal but also creates a welcoming oasis. With the perfect blend of functionality and style, this home offers the best of both convenience and comfort. Welcome to your new home!

Stainless steel refrigerator currently in kitchen, security system and cameras are excluded and do not convey. Refrigerator currently in garage will convey with the home.
